    <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, smartphone, or other devices) when you visit a website. They help the website remember your preferences and enhance your browsing experience. Cookies can be used for various purposes, including remembering login information, tracking website usage, and personalizing content.</p>

    <h2>2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
